    <j.0:title xml:lang="en">Proposal for a&amp;#13;
COUNCIL DECISION&amp;#13;
on the signing, on behalf of the European Union and its Member States, and provisional&amp;#13;
application of a Protocol amending the Euro-Mediterranean Aviation Agreement&amp;#13;
between the European Union and its Member States, of the one part, and the&amp;#13;
government of the State of Israel, of the other part, to take account of the accession to&amp;#13;
the European Union of the Republic of Croatia</j.0:title>
